gr.interamerican.bo2.creation.annotations
Annotation Type DelegateProperties

@Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Documented
public @interface DelegateProperties

Marks a field for creating delegates to some of his properties. If the value attribute of this annotation is empty or null, then all properties of the annotated field will be exposed to the interface of the containing class via delegates.

Required Element Summary
 String[] value
          Defines the properties of this object that constitute the key.
 

Element Detail

value

public abstract String[] value
Defines the properties of this object that constitute the key. The properties are defined separated with commas.

Returns:
Returns the properties that constitute the key.
